name: Grass Eating Cow
description:
Controls: WASD or IJKL/Up Left Right Down Arrow (P2) + Space or Enter/Enter Numpad(P2)

Goal: Produce enough milk so the farmer will not unleash his wrath on you. Scoring points will give you more time, but as time goes on, the timer will go down faster. Eating the different fruits will net you bonus points.

Foes: 

Wolf - Will chase you and temporarily disable movement if hit. If you are stuck make sure to ask a friend for help!

Crow - Flies around the map and eats fruits that it can get to. Make sure to eat it before the crow gets there.

Voice Actors/Credits:

Trent Ku (Almond)

Zachary Buenviaje (Dinosaur, Goat)

Ronald Encanto (Cow, Mooshroom)
